Description: OpenNebula COGNIT Optimizer daemon
 The COGNIT Optimizer is a daemon that optimizes device-to-cluster
 assignments in the COGNIT Framework using linear programming.
 .
 This package includes a bundled Python virtual environment with all
 required dependencies.

